fr.curie.cd2sbgnml.xmlcdwrappers

Class AliasWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.curie.cd2sbgnml.xmlcdwrappers.AliasWrapper

  • public class AliasWrapper
extends Object
    Wraps speciesAlias and complexSpeciesAlias xml entities as they have a lot in common. Compartments are too different and are treated separately.
